games.description: Get ready for an exciting stickman adventure! You will enter an exciting survival battlefield.Fight nervous battles against increasing enemies constantly. Collect experience points and progress through endless waves of enemies. Each wave of enemies is more challenging, so be careful to upgrade your skills to survive! Collect energy boosters in battle to upgrade your stickman skills. Increase speed, increase attack or increase defense.
games.instructions: Mouse click or tap to play

games.description: Get ready for an intense crash battle! Build and customize your tiny vehicles with sharp weapons to defeat opponents. Strategize by choosing the right wheels and weapons. In each round, make precise moves to outmaneuver your rival—smash their vehicle to advance. Keep battling until you lose, then restart and upgrade your weapons using collected coins. The stronger you get, the more challenges you conquer. Let the crash war begin!
games.instructions: - Build your incredible combat vehicle - Compete against enemies, win the battle and earn coins - Unlock the new weapons using coins and upgrade your vehicle - In game health bar for vehicle

games.description: Hey kids! Are you ready for a thrilling island survival adventure? In Survival Island, you’ll explore a mysterious island full of surprises! Cut down trees with your axe, mine rocks, gather grass, and fish to keep your energy up. Produce food to stay strong and upgrade your skills to survive longer. Whether it’s day, night, or stormy, anything can happen! Explore caves, swim, and boost your speed and capacity. Get ready for a fun-filled survival journey in Survival Island!
games.instructions: The game Survival Island is controlled using mouse movements, allowing players to navigate, interact, and explore the island with ease.

games.description: A game in the sorting genre, but in the form of sorting frogs, great graphics, very many levels, and a large variety of frogs. Several variations of levels. Pass levels, get achievements, unlock new kinds of frogs!
games.instructions: Frogs scattered all over the logs, you need to collect 4 identical frogs on the same log. To do this, click or tap on the desired log to select the desired frogs, they will be highlighted. Next, click on another log on which you want to move the frog. If the conditions are met, the frog will jump to the new location. When 4 identical frogs gather on the log, they will run away and you will get a reward.

games.description: This is a mobile phone case game that was designed. Have you ever wanted to create a fashion phone case of your own? In the game, you can show your creativity, enjoy the art of customisation and see your phone evolve the way you like. You can choose your favourite colours, draw, mix, and spray paint your phone case.
games.instructions: Mouse click or tap to play

games.description: Welcome to Royal Bubble Blast, where you'll be transported to a majestic castle to enjoy a royal Bubble Shooter experience! Featuring vibrant, handcrafted designs and a colourful, lively theme, this game offers endless, relaxing gameplay accompanied by a beautiful soundtrack. Play as a King or Queen in the most exclusive Bubble Shooter enjoyed by royalty. Dive into a world of colourful bubbles and endless fun. So, what are you waiting for? Join the royals and start popping!
games.instructions: The goal of Royal Bubble Blast is to clear the board by matching three or more bubbles of the same colour. Aim using your mouse or finger, then shoot to pop the bubbles. The more you pop in a single shot, the higher your score. Avoid too many misses, as fouls will add a new line of bubbles at the top. Keep the bubbles from reaching the bottom of the screen for as long as you can. Keep popping and enjoy the fast-paced fun!

game_info.title: Bottle challenge
game_info.publisher: Shenzhen haikuo yuntour rede tecnologia co., LTD

games.description: This is a puzzle game, the game provides different volumes of the kettle, according to the game level prompts each kettle needs a different magnitude, to reach the required magnitude of the prompt can be cleared
games.instructions: The main control of the game is to click on the water bottle to pour water into another water bottle

games.description: Merge Gun: FPS Shooting Zombie's main mission is to shoot down all coming undead creatures before they kill you. Before you join the battle, you can buy more guns and merge the same guns into new advanced ones. With more powerful and fast ammo in the clip, you can deal with incoming enemies more easily. Both zombies and crows will move forward to you even if you are still reloading. Keep calm and shoot the explosive oil cans on the ground if necessary.
games.instructions: Mouse click or tap to play

games.description: Imagine the beautiful Princess Marie standing in front of a mirror, looking at her reflection. Her eyes are shining, and a sly smile plays on her lips. She is ready to put on an outfit that will emphasize her grace and charm. But then her lover appears and frowns: «My dear, are you really going to wear such an open dress?» Marie knows that her faithful knight sometimes takes too much care of her, but today she intends to look dazzling!
games.instructions: Help Princess Marie create a bright and daring outfit, but do not quarrel with her jealous lover. Combine bold challenge and quiet modesty in a single fashionable look! The result can be saved as a PNG image. Depending on the gaming device, a computer mouse click or a simple touch on touch screens is used to control it.

games.description: In Ball Dunk Fall, your challenge is to guide a constantly falling ball through hoops of varying difficulties by tapping the screen. Test your precision and reflexes as you navigate through tricky obstacles. With each successful dunk, experience the thrill of victory and aim for high scores!
games.instructions: Objective: Pass the ball through as many hoops as possible while avoiding obstacles. Controls: Tap the screen to control the ball's direction as it falls. Gameplay: Time your taps to aim for the hoops. Avoid falling out of bounds and hitting obstacles to keep the game going.

games.description: Block Craft 3D is a first-person RPG game with 3D pixel Minecraft models. Starting from a block base, you can attack the monsters outside to claim diamonds with weapons. I strongly suggest you build bombs to destroy terrains or build blocks to make yourself safe. When you earn enough diamonds, you can unlock and use 4 Melee weapons, 11 guns, and 8 bombs in the store. Glad you will have a good time in this block world.
games.instructions: Mouse click or tap to play

games.description: Two cute sheep must jump from island to island in the sky to escape from the farmers and reach the portal. They need to work together as a team to overcome obstacles. You must help them. Be careful of the obstacles that fall from the ground and sky. The farmers are looking for you, and they want to catch you, so jump over them to escape. If the path is clear, eat all the hay you find. Gather all the hay and safely reach the portal.
games.instructions: *Move using the "WASD" keys and "Arrow Keys." *You can jump twice in a row. *Safely guide both sheep to the portal. *Playable on both mobile and PC.

basic_info.name: Brain Test: One Line Draw Puzzle

game_info.title: Brain Test: One Line Draw Puzzle

games.description: In this engaging one-line puzzle game, challenge your brain by drawing shapes in a single stroke without lifting your finger. Each level presents a unique shape that must be drawn in one continuous line, testing your logic and creativity. With increasing difficulty, you’ll need to plan your moves carefully to solve each puzzle. Perfect for players of all ages, this game offers hours of fun while improving problem-solving skills. Can you master the art of drawing each shape in one go?
games.instructions: 1-Tap and hold to start drawing. 2-Draw the shape in one continuous line. 3-Do not lift your finger until the shape is complete. 4-If you make a mistake, restart and try again. 5-Complete each level by finishing the shape in one stroke.

games.description: In Color Maze your mission is to light up all the paths on the map to complete a level. Make the right move, avoiding obstacles or just pay attention to not get stuck in a corner. Beat all the 20 levels with increasing difficulty to show yourself that you are the real king of Color Maze. Remember, if a level is to hard for you, you can always skip it clicking or touching the reward button in the up right corner of the screen.
games.instructions: WASD or ARROWS to move

games.description: Explore 6 charming bakery shops in this fun hidden object game! With 24 exciting levels, find 6 hidden bakery items in each shop before time runs out. Perfect for all ages, enjoy the challenge and discover delicious treats in every corner. Can you find them all before time runs out?
games.instructions: Use your mouse or tap the screen to select hidden bakery items scattered throughout the shop. Scroll with your mouse to explore different sections of the shop and discover all the hidden treats.

games.description: Ink Inc Tattoo is a free online simulation game for boys played on PuzzleGame. In the game, you can experience the satisfaction of a tattoo artist drawing various artistic tattoos for clients. You need to draw the correct lines and colors to complete the image given by the customer. Mobile, Tablet, and Desktop are playable. Come and get a new entertainment experience.
games.instructions: Mouse or tap to play

games.description: Are you ready for a competitive game between the mummy and the pumpkin king on Halloween? Yes, someone has to win on Halloween! Team up with a friend and choose to be either the mummy or the pumpkin king. Collect as many flying pumpkins as you can! You can earn money by eating candies, and by gathering all the pumpkins, you can win the game. Catch the balloons and take them to the treasure chest. The one who collects and brings them back the fastest wins.
games.instructions: *Use the 'WASD' keys and the 'Arrow Keys' to move. *Playable on both mobile and PC. *Four different hats available in the shop. *The player who collects 10 pumpkins the fastest wins.

games.description: Experience fashion fun like never before with the Shopaholic Black Friday game! Navigate through makeup products, and indulge in chic fashion pieces. Hit the mall, shop as many items as you can before the time runs out, and then return for another styling adventure. Explore an array of lipstick hues, experiment with smoky eyes, or go for colorful shadows, and browse through fashionable dresses, trendy tops, and stylish shoes. Complete the look with dazzling accessories and designer bags.
games.instructions: Use your mouse to play this game on desktops or tap to play on mobile devices.

games.description: Play the new 2048 game with unique mechanics! Develop strategies to clear cubes in endless mode or rescue the monkey. Challenge yourself now!
games.instructions: Click on any cube and then on the same cube next to it. The cubes will connect into a cube of the best level. Save the monkey or just get into the top of the best.

games.description: In Pursuit Rampage, you’re behind the wheel of a police car in an endless, high-speed chase. Navigate through busy streets, dodge obstacles, and close in on criminals while keeping your cool under pressure. The game constantly pushes your reflexes to the limit, with each second offering a new challenge. Whether you're weaving through traffic or speeding down back alleys, the action never lets up.
games.instructions: WASD/Arrow to Drive H for Horn C for Camera

games.description: This thrilling arcade game is designed for adventure enthusiasts and fans of active gameplay. Step into the role of a fearless rolling character, racing through dynamic levels filled with vibrant settings and exhilarating obstacles. With easy-to-master controls, you’ll quickly dive into the action, experiencing a blend of tension and adrenaline. Each level features diverse obstacles and traps, ensuring every run feels fresh and exciting.
games.instructions: Controls for computer: -Left mouse button - move forward - Right mouse button - move backward Controls for phone: - Right side of the screen - move forward - Left side of the screen - move backward

games.description: Now that Halloween is here, the gloomiest day of the year, it's time to bring back the courageous white stickman who is an expert at vanquishing monsters. Stop procrastinating and start enjoying Stickman Halloween Survive right now on your preferred mobile device. It's a fun and free online game. Every living thing on Earth is frightened to death when monsters emerge from their underground lairs on Halloween night.
games.instructions: Instructions: Help the stickman aim his weapon at the right time to shoot the monsters located on different mobile platforms. Controls: Use the mouse to aim and shoot or touch and drag on mobile screens.

games.description: Sprint, Jump and Blast your way through Monster Dash, an action-packed game by the creators of Jetpack Joyride and Fruit Ninja. Join Barry Steakfries and his iconic Machine Gun Jetpack in a world full of menacing monster mayhem, as you run and gun your way through hordes of zombies, vampires and more with the most explosive and powerful weapons you can find!
games.instructions: Experience the classic game resurrected from the dead! With simple controls, just two buttons, making it easy-to-learn but hard to master.

games.description: Meet colorful and diverse mushrooms! Collect mushroom blocks, earn points and win the rankings! On the way you will encounter all kinds of obstacles: lightning, bombs, frozen cells and others. Try to overcome all obstacles and hold out as long as possible, plunging into the cozy atmosphere of mushroom picking, accompanied by pleasant music!
games.instructions: Move the blocks with your finger or mouse. The row will be destroyed if all the cells in it are filled. Use boosters to make it easier to play, and also keep a close eye on the special mushroom blocks! You will lose if the blocks reach the topmost row. Have a good game!

games.description: There has been an outbreak of a zombie virus on a space station. The first group of mercenaries has disappeared. Your task is to find survivors among the zombies and find out the cause of the zombie apocalypse. You will have to fight with a horde of zombies, using different types of weapons. Look for hidden weapons in chests. Upgrade characters and weapons! Use your characters' abilities in heated battles against zombies. Play with a friend on the same device or alone!
games.instructions: The goal of the game is to destroy all zombies and monsters. Find new weapons in the boxes. Upgrade characters and weapons to defeat strong enemies. Q (K) - change weapons; W, A, S, D (arrows) - move; E (M) - apply / activate; F (J) - super weapon. LeftCntrl, Space (RightControl, KeyPad 0) - shooting; Mouse - look / shoot; For mobile devices, use touch input.

games.description: Day of Atrocity is a voxel action game where you play as the hero, battling a relentless swarm of enemies that spawn at an increasing pace. Your objective is to stop them from overtaking the map by wiping them out before they dominate the entire space.
games.instructions: Controls: Control movement with WASD keys Dash with L key Attack with O and P keys Tab key to change character

games.description: Dive into an exhilarating journey through a treacherous cave! Your mission: reach the portal at the end of each level while avoiding deadly spikes and obstacles. With six progressively harder levels, you’ll need sharp reflexes and spot-on timing to survive. Can you conquer every challenge and make it out of the cave? Put your skills to the test in this high-speed action game!
games.instructions: PC controls: LEFT MOUSE BUTTON or SPACEBAR ─ arrow movement MOBILE controls: TOUCHING THE SCREEN ─ arrow movement

games.description: • This is a game in which you have to connect wooden blocks! In the game you have a playing area where you must connect blocks to fill the line! Once the line is full, the blocks will disappear, giving you the most points! Compete with friends or colleagues on the leaderboard! Enjoy your game!
games.instructions: 1. At first it will be easy to connect the blocks, but over time there will be more and more of them. Connect wisely so you have room! 2. Press and hold your finger or mouse to control the block. Release your finger or click the mouse to make the block fall onto the field 3. Enjoy the game!

games.description: Unleash chaos in Stick Boy: Bazooka War! Blast through levels with a variety of powerful bazookas, each with unique abilities. Obliterate enemies, destroy bases, and demolish everything in your path. Choose the perfect ammo to send ragdoll foes flying and experience thrilling destruction as you crush their strongholds. Help Stick Boy annihilate all adversaries and conquer every level in this explosive adventure!
games.instructions: Hold down your finger on the screen or press and hold the Left Mouse Button to take aim. Release to fire.

games.description: Play Word Rivers - an exciting word game where you can enjoy a sea of words and fantastic crosswords. Find words from letters and discover the wonders of the world and words right now!
games.instructions: Playing and guessing words from the world of letters is very simple. Look at the crossword and try to find words by forming them from the letters at the bottom of the screen. Combine the letters in the circle at the bottom by swiping your finger on mobile devices. On a computer, click the first letter in the circle at the bottom, and without releasing the mouse button, move the mouse toward the following letter of the new word.

games.description: Challenge yourself and hunt beautiful animals in stunningly luscious woods. The calming sounds of the forest and lovely graphics will capture your heart. Feel like a true hunter in the unconquered wilderness!
games.instructions: Shoot the animals and collect their trophies in all the different levels to progress to the next region. Unlock and upgrade your hunting gear using the gold you get as a reward.

games.description: Join the penguin’s adventure in Penguin Adventure! You will play as a penguin who must reach the castle in each level. You will explore three worlds, each with its own challenges and surprises. You will also have to control the penguin’s actions. You will collect stars and hearts along the way, which will affect your score and rewards. You will need enough yellow stars to unlock the next world. Penguin Adventure is a game that will test your reaction and strategy. Don’t miss this fun game!
games.instructions: On PC Up and Down arrows = jump and move down J = Throw bullets On Mobile Tap buttons = move.

games.description: Click on groups of two or more candies to destroy them. You need to collect certain amount of different sweets on every level. Wooden blocks, honey and jam should be cleared from the game field. If there is a key on the game field it should be dropped down. The moves are limited for each level. If you have hard time with a task you can use bonuses that can be received when you collect jam.
games.instructions: Destroy tiles by tapping on a group of them.

games.description: Obby is skateboarding on the rooftops and performing dangerous tricks. He wants to skateboard on the rooftops during Halloween. Help Obby reach the finish line safely. You must be very careful! Since it's Halloween, the city is flooded with toxic water, and if you fall from the building, you will die. Jump from barrels to containers and climb to the top of the building. Collect all the pumpkins along the way to earn money. Gather all the pumpkins and reach the finish line!
games.instructions: *Use the 'WASD' keys to move. *15 different levels with unique challenges. *Collect all the pumpkins. *You can buy 4 different costumes from the shop.

games.description: This is an addictive elimination merge puzzle game. If you like synthetic elimination games, then this game is for you. They can remove a portion of the weapons that didn't merge, but there's only one free shot. Be careful, you have to score as many points as possible within the time limit, otherwise, you will have to start another game. Now join the challenging world of the game.
games.instructions: Mouse click or tap to play

games.description: Feel the thrill as racing cars zoom by at lightning speed on the track! Get your hands on these incredible cars and watch them blaze across the raceway. Show off your passion for speed and excitement by collecting them all! How many will you collect? Play now and find out!
games.instructions: Use coins to purchase a car. Tap and drag the cars together to create a more flashy car. Continue merging cars to discover new, more exciting cars. Cars on the race track will start gathering coins for you as time passes.

games.description: Welcome to Little Lily Halloween Prep. It’s time to celebrate Halloween with Little Lily! Enjoy a memorable Halloween night with Lily and play fun-packed Halloween games and activities. Help the lily to complete her makeover, then help her with Halloween face painting. Browse her wardrobe and pick cute outfits and costumes. Finally, help her with cake decoration. A lot more to enjoy and explore this Halloween season with Little Lily. Happy Halloween!!
games.instructions: Left Mouse Button Click or Tap to play

games.description: Welcome to Duet Cats Halloween Cat Music, a game feast for 2 players filled with fun and music!Join your friends in this Halloween-inspired game to challenge the cat's music and have fun! With the rhythm of the music, control the cute cat to move. Let them eat more ice cream. You can choose a different musical challenge. You should accurately move to collect ice cream, and get the highest high score!
games.instructions: Mouse click or tap to play

games.description: An educational and exciting game in which you can test your logical and strategic thinking. Solve unique puzzles to while away the time and relax with excellent soundtrack. A bright and exciting game is perfect not only for children, but will also give you the opportunity to test your skills in solving difficult problems for adults.
games.instructions: Release all the wooden parts so that they fall down! Unscrew the bolts by pressing on them, and screw them into the free holes. When there are no wooden planks left, the level will be completed. Use auxiliary tools: - screwdriver: removes the bolt you press; - freeze time: stops the timer for 30 seconds.
